## Coding Standards

### TypeScript
```typescript
// ✅ DO: Explicit types, interfaces for objects
interface Pet {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  species: 'dog' | 'cat' | 'other';
}

// ❌ DON'T: any, implicit returns
